data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_0e35ca9e69579f670069a67e29547c8196b65fcfcdc1f8a272","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":142,"text":"Nice to meet you, Mizzenmast! How would you like me to address you? Do you have a preferred pronoun?\n\nWhat would you like to do today? I can help with a lot of things, for example:\n- Answer questions or explain topics\n- Brainstorm ideas or plan something (a trip, project, story)\n- Write or edit text (letters, emails, fiction, poetry)\n- Learn a new skill or topic\n- Solve puzzles or practice coding\n- Talk about sailing, ships, knots, weather, or navigation\n\nIf you’re feeling nautical, we could start with a quick chat about your favorite voyage or dream destination. What sounds good?"}

